<h3 id="lab">Lab</h3>
<p>Our research group is part of <a href="http://bits.lab.uic.edu">BITS lab</a>. BITS lab has researchers who are interested various topics related to networking, systems, and security.</p>

<p><img src="../img/lab.jpg" style="float:right;width:300px;" /></p>

